Class GenericListModel<T extends Searchable<T>>

java.lang.Object
javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
cop3330.misc.GenericListModel<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements stored in the underlying GenericList; must implement Searchable with the same type parameter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, TableModel
Direct Known Subclasses:
CourseListModel, StudentListModel
public abstract class GenericListModel<T extends Searchable<T>> extends AbstractTableModel
An abstract table model backed by a generic GenericList of elements that implement the Searchable interface.

This class provides a base implementation of a TableModel where the data is stored in a GenericList of type T. It handles basic table behaviors such as row and column counts and disables cell editing. Subclasses must provide the column names by implementing getColumns().
